{"tid":1319911,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國外交部：中央堅定挺林鄭 斥外媒報道失實","createTime":"2019-07-15T09:12:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-15T10:41:05.000Z","uid":212626,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"963d2575b7c994bde34b39b9aabe70678298c20c","tid":1319911,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T09:12:59.000Z","msg":"英國《金融時報》(Financial Times)引述消息人士報道，特首林鄭月娥在最近數星期本港發生多次大型示威期間，曾不止一次向中央政府提出請辭，但被北京拒絕，並要求她留任以處理善後工作。<br />\n<br />\n外交部駐港公署發言人針對個別西方媒體捕風捉影、散布不實消息，表示強烈不滿和堅決反對，並提出嚴正交涉。<br />\n<br />\n公署表示，中央政府堅定支持林鄭月娥行政長官和特區政府依法施政，維護國家主權、安全和發展利益，維護香港長期繁榮穩定。<br />\n<br />\n公署強烈敦促有關媒體秉持新聞職業操守，停止散布子虛烏有的假消息，以負責任的態度客觀、公正、平衡地進行報道。<br />\n<br />\n此外，外交部發言人耿爽回應指出，沒聽到相關情況，強調中央政府堅定支持特區政府及林鄭月娥依法施政。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2191662/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F2191662%2F&d=Nl%2Bce6%2FxXxAB2W4e8qnvdo5RPfZ%2FgKFUZzIsJfjgB6g%3D&h=2727db2a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2191662/</a>"},{"pid":"862e1eb388f294e3f581a724ecffad20e2517333","tid":1319911,"uid":744,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T09:14:40.000Z","msg":"覆得咁快仲唔係身有屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b25580791c18555a1f30f423a0f333a46ff03f80","tid":1319911,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T09:15:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b44defbbbb4671019898a49bfe264877daee8cc0","tid":1319911,"uid":260161,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T09:15:43.000Z","msg":"即係方向正確<br />\n可以繼續"},{"pid":"8b19e5b117408e36e1d3f0b7548bb243557193a4","tid":1319911,"uid":8441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T09:15:45.000Z","msg":"FT 一係認fake news, 一係擠牙膏<br />\n<br />\n自己簡<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" cla