br />\n人地有無講錯呀，你自己都認頂住林鄭唔比佢走啦"},{"pid":"f09eb1136d877cb980e2a1bd7c02e59b98f66935","tid":1319911,"uid":62247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T09:33:08.000Z","msg":"敵人反對的<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e38f108ba13a5f973aca42014b51e28f9c3c8bc2","tid":1319911,"uid":62314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T09:33:34.000Z","msg":"中國壞消息盡出，開始轉移視線，見無野屌，自己放風再屌返西媒😂😂😂"},{"pid":"094728b70fcf11c6d78b9e26f3b6110e03025ac7","tid":1319911,"uid":228894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T09:34:07.000Z","msg":"而家都冇人肯上馬...<br />\n點會畀佢走得咁易<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9f13ee193753382ebbfb867945faa08c9c8535b","tid":1319911,"uid":113000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T09:36:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddf76d1e501c95e71d28c5308812f87175e06c2b","tid":1319911,"uid":113000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T09:36:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe6f1e6e6725f3fdbca47ef88ecfce637e15c3f7","tid":1319911,"uid":270798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T09:38:09.000Z","msg":"賣港鵝如果真係要辭職, 只有國務院知, 而我信得過國務院唔會走漏消息, 咁究竟邊個洩密, 除左賣港鵝自己, 我諗唔到第二個<br />\n<br />\n咁賣港鵝點解要咁做, 因為想迫中央再出聲明支持佢, 令佢有籌碼可以同差佬談判, 只要佢在位一日就包庇差佬<br />\n<br />\n但佢自身難保, 佢過唔過到 10.1 國慶都難講, 如果換特首, 成立獨立調查委員會增加民望, 呢個應該係規定動作, 無得走一定做<br />\n<br />\n所謂唔出賣其實就係賣到你盡, 諗清楚前因後果, 同埋換特首時, 遲來的清算, 就知而家應該點做。"},{"pid":"ed566a23f90448a98a1f255005c1a3a5c631cf1a","tid":1319911,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fe6f1e6e6725f3fdbca47ef88ecfce637e15c3f7","tid":1319911,"uid":270798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T09:38:09.000Z","msg":"賣港鵝如果真係要辭職, 只有國務院知, 而我